      <description>Score $ L $ $$ L = -E + w_F \frac{F^2}{2\Delta F} + w_S S. $$ Symbol Note $$ E $$ Energy (eV/atom) $$ w_F $$ Weight of the force term. Default: $ w_F = 0.1$ $$ F $$ Averaged norm of the atomic force (eV/Å) $$ \Delta F $$ Absolute difference of $ F $ from the previous step. $ \Delta F = 1$ for the first step. $ \Delta F = 10^{-6}$ if $ \Delta F \le 10^{-6} $.</description>
